          TerraLib 5 - Gdal Data Access Driver
          ==================================================
          
This folder contains an implementation of the Data Access classes
for the Gdal library. 

Driver Dependencies:
--------------------

This driver requires the following modules in order to be built:
1. Common Runtime
2. XML
3. Plugin
4. Data Type
5. SRS
6. Geometry
7. Raster
8. Data Access
9. Memory
10. OGR
11. Raster

The third-party software needed:
1. Gdal
2. Boost.FileSystem
3. Boost.System

More Information:
-----------------

The TerraLib 5 wiki contains a complete explanation about
the internals of this driver:
http://www.dpi.inpe.br/terralib5/wiki/doku.php?id=wiki:designimplementation:dataaccess:drivers:gdal


